{"lemma":"حَوْبَة","slug":"حَوْبَة","root":"ح.#.ب","root_slug":"ح-_-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-_-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n9409","n9410"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n9409","headword_ar":"حَوْبَةٌ","root":"Hwb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuwbN","text_ar":"حُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places.       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Maternal tenderness of heart."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Anxiety;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiybapN","text_ar":"حِيبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Want; poverty; indigence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiybapN","text_ar":"حِيبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawobN","text_ar":"حَوْبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) You say, in prayer,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilayoka A^arofaEu HawobatiY","text_ar":"اـِلَيْكَ اَرْفَعُ حَوْبَتِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"To Thee I make known"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"my want."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA from a trad.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloHaqa A@ll~`hu bihi AlHawobapa","text_ar":"اَلْحَقَ ا@للّٰهُ بِهِ الحَوْبَةَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God bring upon him want,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"poverty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"indigence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * TA.) [And hence,] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aibonu HawobK","text_ar":"اِبْنُ حَوْبٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man oppressed by difficulty, trouble, distress,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adversity; a man in need:"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any man in such a state."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiyaAlu A@boni HawobK","text_ar":"عِيَالُ ا@بْنِ حَوْبٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The family of a man oppressed by difficulty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiybapN","text_ar":"حِيبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) but only used in speaking of an evil state; as in the phrases,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAta biHawobapi suwo'K","text_ar":"بَاتَ بِحَوْبَةِ سُوْءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwo'K","text_ar":"سُوْءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biHiybapi","text_ar":"بِحِيبَةِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He passed the night in an evil state"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-  [Hence also, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw HawobapK","text_ar":"ذُو حَوْبَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAtu HawobapK","text_ar":"ذَاتُ حَوْبَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*awuw HawobapK","text_ar":"ذَوُو حَوْبَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A weak man;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuwbapN","text_ar":"حُوبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a weak woman:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weak persons:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) and ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a man who can neither profit nor harm;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a man having neither good nor evil:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuwabN","text_ar":"حُوَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (AZ, S.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ait~aquwA A@ll~`ha fiY AlHawobaAti","text_ar":"اِتَّقُوا ا@للّٰهَ فِى الحَوْبَاتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*awaAti AlHawobaAti","text_ar":"ذَوَاتِ الحَوْبَاتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fear ye God with respect to the needy women, who cannot do without some one to maintain them, and to take constant care of them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a liY A^aEuwluhaA","text_ar":"اـِنَّ لِى اَعُولُهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily I have a weak family to maintain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A person whom one is under an obligation to respect,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"honour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"defend, and who may be subjected to loss,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ruin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"if abandoned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as a mother,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sister,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"daughter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any other female relation within the prohibited degrees of marriage;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiybapN","text_ar":"حِيبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (ISk, S:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any such relation whom it is sinful to subject to loss,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ruin, by abandoning her:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A 'Obeyd, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mother:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) by some explained peculiarly as having this meaning: (A 'Obeyd, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a  wife;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a concubine;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) because both require to be maintained: (TA:) and, as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawobN","text_ar":"حَوْبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"father and mother:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sister:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a daughter."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liY fiY baniY fulaAnK HawobapK","text_ar":"لِى فِى بَنِى فُلَانٍ حَوْبَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiybapN","text_ar":"حِيبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S, K *) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuwbapN","text_ar":"حُوبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have, among the sons of such a one, a female relation such as any of those above specified:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one to whom I bear relationship on the side of the mother:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a relation within the prohibited degrees of marriage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, TA.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sacred,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an inviolable, right"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a person,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which it would be sinful to disregard;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEalotuhu liHawobapi fulaAnK","text_ar":"فَعَلْتُهُ لِحَوْبَةِ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I did it for the sake of the sacred,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inviolable, right of such a one"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A horse,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"similar beast;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAb~apN","text_ar":"دَابَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) for this, also, cannot do without some one to take constant care of it, and to sustain it. (TA.)       -A3-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"middle of a house."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) Perhaps the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this instance is a substitute for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m","text_ar":"م"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","S","ISk"]},{"entry_id":"n9410","headword_ar":"حُوبَةٌ","root":"Hwb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuwbN","text_ar":"حُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":       -A2-  and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawobapN","text_ar":"حَوْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places.       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuwbapN mina AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"حُوبَةٌ مِنَ الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bad tract of land;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiybapN","text_ar":"حِيبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}